In addition, each model creates an "intelligent" graphic image on which to "click" different parts of the vehicle.
If this is a much-sold model, work can be completed in a week if the procedure is speedy.
If this is a less common car, it may take up to three or four months. Currently, Audatex has 99.2% of the cars distributed in Spain for complete information.
